      "content": "**MEMORANDUM**\n\n**TO:** New Fintech Client Stakeholders\n**FROM:** Compliance Department\n**DATE:** October 26, 2023\n**SUBJECT:** Comprehensive KYC and AML Operational Framework\n\n**1. Executive Summary**\nThis document establishes our rigorous **regulatory compliance** protocols designed to effectively combat **financial crime** and **illicit finance** across all client onboarding and servicing activities. Our strategy is founded on a strict **risk-based approach** that mandates **enhanced due diligence** for high-risk entities, ensuring we meet all **anti-money laundering** mandates while maintaining operational efficiency.\n\n**2. Onboarding and Initial Assessment**\nUpon receipt of a **procurement of documents** request, we immediately initiate **identity verification** and **sanctions screening** for all prospective clients. This process includes mandatory **checking against lists** to prevent **terrorist financing** and ensures that no **politically exposed persons** or **high-risk jurisdiction** entities are onboarded without prior approval. We perform **PEP screening** for all **beneficial ownership** declarations to accurately identify the **ultimate beneficial owner** and verify their **source of funds** and **source of wealth",
